{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/930280/extras/EN_About_This_Game.gif?t=1722245037\" /><br><br>Join the District Crime Agency in this isometric, modern noir deduction thriller. <strong>Explore crime scenes</strong> in complex dioramas, <strong>organize your evidence</strong> effectively, and blur the lines between right and wrong to <strong>present your case</strong>. Do you have what it takes to be a <strong>real detective</strong>?<br><br>On her first day at the DCA, fresh-faced rookie <strong>Cassandra Clarke</strong>, is teamed with a reluctant burnt-out detective, <strong>Nate Huston</strong>, to investigate the murder of a prominent politician. While all evidence points to a botched robbery, it soon entwines the two detectives into a <strong>complex, interconnected series of crimes</strong> that are anything but an open-and-shut case.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/930280/extras/EN_Investigate_Crime_Scenes.gif?t=1722245037\" /><br><br>Explore <strong>detailed, isometric crime scenes</strong>, navigating perspectives to uncover new clues. <strong>Question suspects</strong> in the area, and <strong>find contradictions</strong> in evidence to catch them out. Can you tell apart the red herrings from the key to the case?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/930280/extras/EN_Organize_Evidence.gif?t=1722245037\" /><br><br>Gather walls of evidence from crime scenes, interviews with suspects, and forensic results. It\u2019s up to you to <strong>keep your workspace organized</strong> so you don\u2019t miss anything, and cut through to the real <strong>who, what, and why</strong>.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/930280/extras/EN_Written_by_Pros.gif?t=1722245037\" /><br><br>Enjoy a <strong>rich and immersive story</strong> inspired by film noir, written by film &amp; TV professionals at BAFTA-winning production company Blazing Griffin. With <strong>complex characters</strong> and <strong>dark, pervasive settings</strong>, expect the unexpected as the scales of justice are tilted.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/930280/extras/EN_Available_On_Tilt5.png?t=1722245037\" /><br><br>Tilt Five owners can experience the game in full AR: investigate the crime scenes like real-world dioramas, peer around corners for hidden clues, and solve murder mysteries from a completely original point-of-view.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Welcome to the DCA","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/930280/96c0acb4287b06807c84e4c747114491dd019f96.jpg"},{"name":"Episode 1 Complete","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/930280/b86b7ab08241734b073f7e6fd323221fd8af8fb1.jpg"},{"name":"Episode 1 Perfect","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/930280/4f7bfb7a4ed8a15390cca4b0a84a7d0ee77ac4fa.jpg"},{"name":"Episode 2 Complete","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/930280/8f1b86f672028c8645f41d13d7b4bb3d71fb15b1.jpg"},{"name":"Episode 2 Perfect","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/930280/b361ff8f363309e29b1b5625697be484730a4531.jpg"},{"name":"Episode 3 Complete","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/930280/98b8a89f4f7501a77cc917cdb6cfc93ca428bd79.jpg"},{"name":"Episode 3 Perfect","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/930280/7dc2c519216ec46bc712a4837336cb33290c0d2b.jpg"},{"name":"Episode 4 Complete","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/930280/46d1a3a7f8d507bdc72dc2abbbc9c6bd714df250.jpg"},{"name":"Epis